data.description: The curb appeal of this home will have you stopping your car and wanting to see more! From the moment you walk through the front door you will be captivated by the entry and dining room leading you into a large kitchen with white cabinets and stainless steel appliances that overlook the cozy family room with a fireplace! Vinyl wood plank flooring throughout the first floor and carpet in the oversized master retreat with a spacious master bath equipped with separate garden tub & shower  along with double sink vanity and ceramic tile flooring. Upstairs there is plenty of room for the kiddos with 3 large secondary bedrooms, game room and a media room that can easily be converted into a 5th bedroom. Fully sodded front yard with fenced backyard with plenty of space for outdoor entertaining! This home includes a Wifi thermostat, USB outlets, garage door opener and much more! Ready Now! Call to see this home today!
